Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: A young Mon Calamari male Padawan was a member of the Jedi Order. At some point, the Padawan attempted to steal the clay figures of Jedi Master Wishan but was scared off by Jedi Knight Jabe Rann's sculpture of a dragon.
